When to use slow and fast?

Version 1

1. to find th emiddle of a linked list
      --> by the time fast reaches to the end, slow is at the middle

2. to detect a cycle
      --> both fast and slow will overlap

3. to find where the cycle starts

Version 2

1. remove nth node from end
    --> fast moves n+1
    --> fast and slow moves together
    --> when fast becomes null then slow will be before the nth node

2. find nth node from end
    --> fast moves n times
    --> slow and fast moves togther
